{"id":30769,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"整个冬天，由于手冻僵了，<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/group/topic/30262\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">画画都不自然</a>，于是暂停。<br>现在感到再不画画可能就不会画了，于是开始了画力复健练习。<br><br>于是从桌上的小物件练起。<br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/60/c4/14382_CCw4l.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>先立的草稿。感觉草稿好渣。想着要不要删稿不画了…<br><br>——但还是磨蹭了半小时…<br><br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/60/c4/14382_pLySa.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>居然完成了。<br><br>这时我突发奇想，对图调了下滤镜…<br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/60/c4/14382_h7aSk.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>这样感觉好像动画/gal的背景小物件…<br><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"http://laoism.lofter.com/post/187236_d8da37\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\"><span style=\"color: Gray;\">此文也有发布于lofter</span></a></p> ","time":"2014-2-9 20:00","title":"为了恢复画力而练习／gal画风速成(伪)","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"(✨️VIP 8✨️)"}